description:
Traffic information for subway/tramway... (Paris and suburbs) This application allows you to consult various traffic information for different RATP/SNCF transport services (for Paris and the suburbs) : • Métro • RER • Tramway
This application is not official and is not endorsed or approved by Île-de-France Mobilités, RATP, SNCF or any other transport network company.
The pictograms of the lines are from Île-de-France Mobilités (https://data.iledefrance-mobilites.fr/explore/dataset/emplacement-des-gares-idf/information/) and are under the "Licence Ouverte v2.0 (Etalab)" license (https://www.etalab.gouv.fr/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/ETALAB-Licence-Ouverte-v2.0.pdf).
